ğŸ¨ COMPONENT LIBRARY SPECIFICATION

Navigation & Layout

```typescript
HeaderComponent {
  logo: 'Quantum Voice AI' with matrix_blue glow,
  navigation: 'Amazon-style mega menu',
  user_menu: 'Google Cloud dropdown',
  status_indicator: 'SpaceX-style system status light'
}

SidebarComponent {
  background: 'carbon_gray with glass effect',
  active_item: 'matrix_blue glow border',
  icons: 'Outlined when inactive, filled when active'
}
```

Data Visualization

```typescript
MetricCard {
  background: 'carbon_gray with subtle grid',
  border: '1px solid steel with matrix_blue glow on hover',
  value: 'Large electric_purple typography',
  trend: 'cyber_green up arrows, neon_pink down arrows'
}

AnalyticsChart {
  theme: 'Dark with matrix_blue primary, cyber_green secondary',
  grid: 'Subtle steel lines',
  tooltips: 'Glass effect with glow'
}
```

Forms & Inputs

```typescript
InputField {
  default: 'carbon_gray background, silver text',
  focus: 'matrix_blue glow border, cyber_green caret',
  error: 'neon_pink glow and text'
}

ButtonSystem {
  primary: 'matrix_blue gradient with glow',
  secondary: 'steel with silver text, glow on hover',
  danger: 'neon_pink gradient with pulse animation'
}
```

