ğŸ“± SPECIFIC PAGE FLOWS

Onboarding Experience (Amazon + Google Cloud inspired)

```
Step 1: Welcome (SpaceX-style hero with mission statement)
Step 2: Campaign Setup (Google Cloud wizard style)
Step 3: AI Agent Training (Interactive voice setup)
Step 4: Integration Connect (Amazon 1-click style)
Step 5: Launch (SpaceX countdown animation)
```

Voice Call Flow (Matrix + Google Duo)

```
1. Ringing: Pulsing holographic circle with matrix_blue glow
2. Active Call: Central transcript with participant avatars
3. AI Thinking: Pulsing cyber_green loader with processing text
4. Handoff: Smooth SpaceX stage separation animation
```

Admin Dashboard (SpaceX Mission Control)

```
Left Panel: System telemetry (calls, cost, performance)
Center: Real-time call map (like rocket trajectory)
Right: Alert panel (mission-critical notifications)
Bottom: Quick action console (launch new campaign, etc.)
```

